"config>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/closest_location.rst:40
msgid "Location names"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/closest_location.rst:42
msgid ""
"To configure location names, begin by navigating "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Locations`. Then, "
"select an existing location, or click :guilabel:`New` to create a new one, "
"and then enter the desired name in the :guilabel:`Location Name` field."
