":guilabel:`Hardware`, và đánh dấu vào ô :guilabel:`Package Contents`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/print_on_validation.rst:292
msgid ""
"If the option is not available, enable the :doc:`Packages <../../"
