msgstr ":guilabel:`Shipping Method`: nhập `Sendcloud DPD`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:129
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Provider`: select :guilabel:`Sendcloud` from the drop-down menu."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Provider`: chọn :guilabel:`Sendcloud` từ menu thả xuống."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:130
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Delivery Product`: set the product that was configured for this "
"shipping method or create a new product."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Delivery Product`: đặt sản phẩm đã được cấu hình cho phương thức "
"vận chuyển này hoặc tạo sản phẩm mới."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:132
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`SendCloud Configuration` tab, enter "
