msgstr ""
":icon:`fa-refresh` :guilabel:`Bổ sung hàng`: truy cập trang :doc:`quy tắc "
"tái đặt hàng <../replenishment/reordering_rules>` để bổ sung sản phẩm tại vị "
"trí cụ thể."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/reporting/locations.rst:57
msgid ""
"In the upper-left corner of the page, click the :guilabel:`New` button to "
"make an :doc:`inventory adjustment <../inventory_management/count_products>` "
"to record quantities of a certain product at a specific :guilabel:`Location`."
msgstr ""
